    <section>
      <title>Release Strategy</title>

      <para>Cut release branch.</para>

<programlisting>
$ svn copy &#45;-username marayl \
   https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/aug/trunk \
   https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/aug/branches/releng-0.5
</programlisting>

      <para>Check-out release branch.</para>

<programlisting>
$ svn checkout &#45;-username marayl \
   https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/aug/branches/releng-0.5 \
   aug
</programlisting>

      <para>Bump version number in <filename>configure.in</filename> and
      <filename>Doxyfile</filename>.</para>

      <para>Configure using maintainer mode.</para>

      <para>Build with checks.</para>

      <para>Update images.</para>

      <para>Tag release, e.g. rel-0.5.rc1</para>

<programlisting>
$ svn copy &#45;-username marayl \
   https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/aug/branches/releng-0.5 \
   https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/aug/tags/rel-0.5.rc1
</programlisting>

      <para>Build source distribution using the <command>make dist</command>
      command.</para>

      <para>Build binaries and documentation from source.</para>

      <para>Release files to sourceforge.</para>

      <para>Tag release, e.g. rel-0.5.0</para>      

<programlisting>
$ svn copy &#45;-username marayl \
   https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/aug/tags/rel-0.5.rc1 \
   https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/aug/tags/rel-0.5.0
</programlisting>

